{
  "video_id": "xp0O2vi8DX4",
  "title": "How to motivate yourself to change your behavior | Tali Sharot | TEDxCambridge",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Leonardo Silva Reviewer: Denise RQ"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15157.0,
      "end_time": 17910.0,
      "text": "So, we all have some behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17910.0,
      "end_time": 20500.0,
      "text": "that we would like to change about ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20500.0,
      "end_time": 22899.0,
      "text": "And we certainly all want to help someone else"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22899.0,
      "end_time": 25523.0,
      "text": "change their behavior in a positive way."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25523.0,
      "end_time": 28666.0,
      "text": "So, maybe it&#39;s your kid, your spouse, your colleague."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29326.0,
      "end_time": 31445.0,
      "text": "So I want to share some new research with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31445.0,
      "end_time": 34293.0,
      "text": "that I think reveals something really important"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34293.0,
      "end_time": 38920.0,
      "text": "about what gets people to change their behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38572.0,
      "end_time": 41596.0,
      "text": "But before I do that, let&#39;s zoom in on one strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41596.0,
      "end_time": 44297.0,
      "text": "that I think you probably use a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44297.0,
      "end_time": 47690.0,
      "text": "So, let&#39;s say you&#39;re trying to stop yourself from snacking."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47691.0,
      "end_time": 49519.0,
      "text": "What do you tell yourself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49909.0,
      "end_time": 52482.0,
      "text": "Well, most people, in a monologue, will say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52482.0,
      "end_time": 54548.0,
      "text": "\"Beware. You&#39;ll be fat.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54928.0,
      "end_time": 58388.0,
      "text": "And if this was your kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59600.0,
      "end_time": 62640.0,
      "text": "you would probably tell him that smoking kills"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62640.0,
      "end_time": 65750.0,
      "text": "and, by the way, he&#39;s in big, big trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65750.0,
      "end_time": 66374.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66374.0,
      "end_time": 68134.0,
      "text": "So, what we&#39;re trying to do here"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68135.0,
      "end_time": 72130.0,
      "text": "is we&#39;re trying to scare ourselves and others"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72130.0,
      "end_time": 73810.0,
      "text": "into changing their behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73810.0,
      "end_time": 75401.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just us."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75401.0,
      "end_time": 81149.0,
      "text": "Warnings and threats are really common in health campaigns, in policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81509.0,
      "end_time": 85390.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because we all share this deep-rooted belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85390.0,
      "end_time": 89191.0,
      "text": "that if you threaten people, if fear is induced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89191.0,
      "end_time": 91367.0,
      "text": "it will get them to act."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91367.0,
      "end_time": 94490.0,
      "text": "And it seems like a really reasonable assumption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94719.0,
      "end_time": 97401.0,
      "text": "except for the fact that the science shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97402.0,
      "end_time": 102207.0,
      "text": "that warnings have very limited impact on behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102207.0,
      "end_time": 105556.0,
      "text": "So, graphic images on cigarette packets, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105556.0,
      "end_time": 107678.0,
      "text": "do not deter smokers from smoking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107678.0,
      "end_time": 110542.0,
      "text": "and one study found that, after looking at those images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110542.0,
      "end_time": 113722.0,
      "text": "quitting actually became a lower priority for smokers."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113722.0,
      "end_time": 116360.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m not saying that warnings and threats never work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116361.0,
      "end_time": 120128.0,
      "text": "but what I&#39;m saying is, on average, they seem to have a very limited impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120128.0,
      "end_time": 122546.0,
      "text": "And so, the question is: why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122546.0,
      "end_time": 124697.0,
      "text": "Why are we resistant to warnings?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125350.0,
      "end_time": 128204.0,
      "text": "Well, if you think about animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128205.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130495.00000000001,
      "text": "when you induce fear in an animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130495.0,
      "end_time": 135617.0,
      "text": "the most common response you will see is freezing or fleeing;"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135957.0,
      "end_time": 137900.0,
      "text": "fighting, not as much."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 137901.0,
      "end_time": 139799.0,
      "text": "And so, humans are the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139799.0,
      "end_time": 141395.0,
      "text": "So if something scares us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141395.0,
      "end_time": 144966.0,
      "text": "we tend to shut down and we try to eliminate the negative feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144966.0,
      "end_time": 146732.0,
      "text": "So, we might use rationalizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146732.0,
      "end_time": 148849.0,
      "text": "For example, you might tell yourself:"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148849.0,
      "end_time": 151346.0,
      "text": "\"My grandpa smoked. He lived to be 90."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151347.0,
      "end_time": 155124.0,
      "text": "So, I have really good genes and absolutely nothing to worry about.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155124.0,
      "end_time": 159300.0,
      "text": "And this process can actually make you feel more resilient"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159300.0,
      "end_time": 160668.0,
      "text": "than you did before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 160669.0,
      "end_time": 164770.0,
      "text": "which is why warnings sometimes have this boomerang effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168207.0,
      "text": "In other times, we simply put our head in the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168207.0,
      "end_time": 169678.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 169678.0,
      "end_time": 171436.0,
      "text": "Take the stock market for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171437.0,
      "end_time": 174102.0,
      "text": "Do you know when people pull their head out of the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174102.0,
      "end_time": 175487.0,
      "text": "to look at their accounts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 175487.0,
      "end_time": 179154.0,
      "text": "not to make a transaction, just to log in to check their account?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 179154.0,
      "end_time": 181609.0,
      "text": "So, what you&#39;re seeing here, in black,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 181609.0,
      "end_time": 185236.0,
      "text": "is the S&P 500 over two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185236.0,
      "end_time": 187105.0,
      "text": "and in gray, is the number of times"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187105.0,
      "end_time": 189916.0,
      "text": "that people logged in  to their account just to check."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189916.0,
      "end_time": 192418.0,
      "text": "And this is data from Karlsson, Loewenstein & Seppi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192419.0,
      "end_time": 194757.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s control [data] for all the obvious confounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194757.0,
      "end_time": 196105.0,
      "text": "So, what do we see?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196105.0,
      "end_time": 199686.0,
      "text": "When the market is high, people log in all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200424.0,
      "end_time": 203144.0,
      "text": "because positive information makes you feel good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 203144.0,
      "end_time": 205170.0,
      "text": "so you seek it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 205170.0,
      "end_time": 206946.0,
      "text": "And when the market is low,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 206946.0,
      "end_time": 208859.0,
      "text": "people avoid logging in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 208860.0,
      "end_time": 211319.0,
      "text": "because negative information makes us feel bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211319.0,
      "end_time": 213787.0,
      "text": "so we try to avoid it altogether."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 214588.0,
      "end_time": 216618.0,
      "text": "And all this is true"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216618.0,
      "end_time": 221283.0,
      "text": "as long as bad information can reasonably be avoided."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221283.0,
      "end_time": 224640.0,
      "text": "So, what you don&#39;t see here is what happened a few months later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224640.0,
      "end_time": 226679.0,
      "text": "in the financial collapse of 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 226680.0,
      "end_time": 228738.0,
      "text": "when the market went drastically down"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228738.0,
      "end_time": 231929.0,
      "text": "and that was when people started logging in frantically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231929.0,
      "end_time": 233986.0,
      "text": "but it was a bit too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234689.0,
      "end_time": 238285.0,
      "text": "So, you can think about it like this -- it&#39;s not just finance:"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238285.0,
      "end_time": 240543.0,
      "text": "In many different parts of our life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 240543.0,
      "end_time": 242102.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243400.0,
      "end_time": 246897.0,
      "text": "we have warning signs and bad behaviors now."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 246897.0,
      "end_time": 252321.0,
      "text": "And they could potentially lead to all these bad outcomes later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 252321.0,
      "end_time": 254299.0,
      "text": "but not necessarily so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 254299.0,
      "end_time": 257776.0,
      "text": "because there are different routs from your present to your future, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 257776.0,
      "end_time": 260252.0,
      "text": "It can go this way, it can go that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260252.0,
      "end_time": 262216.0,
      "text": "And, as time passes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 262216.0,
      "end_time": 266370.0,
      "text": "you gather more and more information about where the wind is blowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 266370.0,
      "end_time": 267940.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 267940.0,
      "end_time": 270578.0,
      "text": "And, at any point, you can intervene"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 270578.0,
      "end_time": 273286.0,
      "text": "and you could potentially change the outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 273286.0,
      "end_time": 275676.0,
      "text": "but that takes energy and you might tell yourself:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 275676.0,
      "end_time": 278936.0,
      "text": "\"What&#39;s the point about worrying about something that might happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 278936.0,
      "end_time": 280520.0,
      "text": "It might not happen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 281236.0,
      "end_time": 283255.0,
      "text": "Until we reach this point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 283255.0,
      "end_time": 287704.0,
      "text": "at which time you do jump into action, but sometimes it&#39;s a little bit too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 288764.0,
      "end_time": 290712.0,
      "text": "So, we wanted to know, in my lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 290712.0,
      "end_time": 294174.0,
      "text": "what type of information does leak into people."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 294174.0,
      "end_time": 295745.0,
      "text": "So, we conducted an experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 295745.0,
      "end_time": 300449.0,
      "text": "where we asked approximately 100 people to estimate the likelihood"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 300449.0,
      "end_time": 304670.0,
      "text": "of 80 different negative events that might happen to them in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 304670.0,
      "end_time": 307580.0,
      "text": "So, for example, I might ask you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 307580.0,
      "end_time": 311700.0,
      "text": "\"What is the likelihood that you&#39;ll suffer hearing loss in your future?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 311450.0,
      "end_time": 314238.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s say you think it&#39;s about 50%."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 314951.0,
      "end_time": 318797.0,
      "text": "Then, I give you the opinion of two different experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 318797.0,
      "end_time": 320814.0,
      "text": "So, expert A tells you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 320814.0,
      "end_time": 324745.0,
      "text": "\"You know, for someone like you, I think it&#39;s only 40%.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 324745.0,
      "end_time": 328298.0,
      "text": "So, they give you a rosier view of your future."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 328844.0,
      "end_time": 330973.0,
      "text": "Expert B says:"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 330973.0,
      "end_time": 332805.0,
      "text": "\"You know, for someone like you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 332805.0,
      "end_time": 335825.0,
      "text": "I actually think it&#39;s about 60%. It&#39;s worse.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 335825.0,
      "end_time": 339614.0,
      "text": "So, they give you a bleaker view of your future."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 339614.0,
      "end_time": 341244.0,
      "text": "What should you do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 342810.0,
      "end_time": 344839.0,
      "text": "Well, you shouldn&#39;t change your beliefs, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 345434.0,
      "end_time": 346434.0,
      "text": "Wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 346434.0,
      "end_time": 349356.0,
      "text": "What we find is that people tend to change their beliefs"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 349356.0,
      "end_time": 352123.0,
      "text": "towards a more desirable opinion."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 353234.0,
      "end_time": 358610.0,
      "text": "In other words, people listen to the positive information."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358942.0,
      "end_time": 363950.0,
      "text": "Now, this study was conducted on college students, so you might say:"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 363950.0,
      "end_time": 366205.0,
      "text": "\"Well, college students are delusional, right? We all know that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 366205.0,
      "end_time": 367159.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 367159.0,
      "end_time": 369905.0,
      "text": "And surely, as we grow older, we grow wiser."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 369905.0,
      "end_time": 372852.0,
      "text": "So we said: \"OK, let&#39;s test that. Does this really generalize?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 372852.0,
      "end_time": 375399.0,
      "text": "Does it generalize  to your kid, to your parent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 375399.0,
      "end_time": 377598.0,
      "text": "Does it generalize to your spouse?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 377598.0,
      "end_time": 381516.0,
      "text": "And so, we tested people from the age of 10 until the age of 80,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 381977.0,
      "end_time": 384554.0,
      "text": "and the answer was yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 384555.0,
      "end_time": 386280.0,
      "text": "In all these age groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 386280.0,
      "end_time": 388467.0,
      "text": "people take in information they want to hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 388468.0,
      "end_time": 391800.0,
      "text": "-- like someone telling you  you&#39;re more attractive than you thought --"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 391800.0,
      "end_time": 394649.0,
      "text": "than information that they don&#39;t want to hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 394649.0,
      "end_time": 397730.0,
      "text": "And the ability to learn from good news"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 397730.0,
      "end_time": 400823.0,
      "text": "remained quite stable throughout the life span,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 401693.0,
      "end_time": 404870.0,
      "text": "but the ability to learn from bad news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 404880.0,
      "end_time": 406514.0,
      "text": "that changes as you age."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 407440.0,
      "end_time": 410214.0,
      "text": "So, what we found was that kids and teenagers"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 410214.0,
      "end_time": 413126.0,
      "text": "were the worse at learning from bad news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 413126.0,
      "end_time": 417630.0,
      "text": "and the ability became better and better as people aged."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 417640.0,
      "end_time": 421104.0,
      "text": "But then, around the age of 40, around midlife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 421104.0,
      "end_time": 423352.0,
      "text": "it started deteriorating again."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 424319.0,
      "end_time": 428126.0,
      "text": "So, what this means  is that the most vulnerable populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 428126.0,
      "end_time": 431702.0,
      "text": "kids and teenagers on the one hand, and the elderly on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 431702.0,
      "end_time": 435676.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re the least likely to accurately learn from warnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 436746.0,
      "end_time": 438176.0,
      "text": "But what you can see here"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 438177.0,
      "end_time": 440188.0,
      "text": "is that it doesn&#39;t matter what age you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 440188.0,
      "end_time": 442781.0,
      "text": "You can be 20, 30, 40, 50 or 60;"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 442781.0,
      "end_time": 445124.0,
      "text": "everyone takes in information they want to hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 445124.0,
      "end_time": 447581.0,
      "text": "more than information that they don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 448321.0,
      "end_time": 451979.0,
      "text": "And so, we end up with a view like this of ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 451979.0,
      "end_time": 453986.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 459883.0,
      "end_time": 465585.0,
      "text": "Our mistake as teachers, as mentors, as employers"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 465585.0,
      "end_time": 468407.0,
      "text": "is that, instead of working with this positive image"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 468408.0,
      "end_time": 471792.0,
      "text": "that people so effortfully maintain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 471792.0,
      "end_time": 474635.0,
      "text": "we try and put a clear mirror in front of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 474635.0,
      "end_time": 475938.0,
      "text": "We tell them: \"You know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 475938.0,
      "end_time": 478700.0,
      "text": "the image is just going to get worse and worse and worse.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 478701.0,
      "end_time": 480467.0,
      "text": "And it doesn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 480467.0,
      "end_time": 485248.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t work because the brain will frantically try to distort the image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 485248.0,
      "end_time": 487921.0,
      "text": "using Photoshop and fancy lenses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 487921.0,
      "end_time": 490868.0,
      "text": "until it gets the image it&#39;s happy with."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 491638.0,
      "end_time": 496361.0,
      "text": "But what would happen if we went along with how our brain works"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 496361.0,
      "end_time": 498294.0,
      "text": "and not against it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 498294.0,
      "end_time": 500671.0,
      "text": "Take handwashing, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 500671.0,
      "end_time": 503742.0,
      "text": "We all know that handwashing is the number one way"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 503742.0,
      "end_time": 505350.0,
      "text": "to prevent the spread of disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 505350.0,
      "end_time": 507717.0,
      "text": "and this is really important in hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 507717.0,
      "end_time": 509995.0,
      "text": "So, in a hospital here in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 509995.0,
      "end_time": 511353.0,
      "text": "a camera was installed"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 511353.0,
      "end_time": 515680.0,
      "text": "to see how often medical staff do, in fact, sanitize their hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 515679.0,
      "end_time": 519197.0,
      "text": "before and after entering  a patient&#39;s room."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 519197.0,
      "end_time": 523337.0,
      "text": "Now, the medical staff knew a camera was installed."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 523337.0,
      "end_time": 527347.0,
      "text": "Nevertheless, only one in ten  washed their hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 527347.0,
      "end_time": 530576.0,
      "text": "before and after entering a patient&#39;s room."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 531836.0,
      "end_time": 534941.0,
      "text": "But then, an intervention was introduced:"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 534941.0,
      "end_time": 536921.0,
      "text": "an electronic board"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 536921.0,
      "end_time": 540610.0,
      "text": "that told the medical staff how well they were doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 540561.0,
      "end_time": 544573.0,
      "text": "Every time you washed your hands, the numbers went up on the screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 544573.0,
      "end_time": 547637.0,
      "text": "and it showed you your rate of your current shift"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 547637.0,
      "end_time": 550936.0,
      "text": "and the rate of the weekly staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 551927.0,
      "end_time": 554726.0,
      "text": "And what happened? Boom."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 554726.0,
      "end_time": 557789.0,
      "text": "Compliance raised to 90%,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 557789.0,
      "end_time": 559833.0,
      "text": "which is absolutely amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 559833.0,
      "end_time": 562680.0,
      "text": "And the research staff  were amazed as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 562680.0,
      "end_time": 566270.0,
      "text": "and they made sure to replicate it in another division in the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 566270.0,
      "end_time": 568694.0,
      "text": "Again, the same results."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 569984.0,
      "end_time": 573725.0,
      "text": "So, why does this intervention work so well?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 575325.0,
      "end_time": 576797.0,
      "text": "It works well"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 576797.0,
      "end_time": 579869.0,
      "text": "because, instead of using warnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 579869.0,
      "end_time": 583802.0,
      "text": "about bad things that can happen in the future, like disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 583802.0,
      "end_time": 590216.0,
      "text": "it uses three principles that we know really drive your mind and your behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 590483.0,
      "end_time": 592316.0,
      "text": "Let me explain."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 592317.0,
      "end_time": 595790.0,
      "text": "The first one is social incentives."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 596670.0,
      "end_time": 598319.0,
      "text": "In the hospital study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 598319.0,
      "end_time": 600996.0,
      "text": "the medical staff could see what other people were doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 600996.0,
      "end_time": 604977.0,
      "text": "They can see the rates of the shift, the rate of the week."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 604979.0,
      "end_time": 608558.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re social people, we really care  what other people are doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 608558.0,
      "end_time": 611600.0,
      "text": "we want to do the same and we want to do it better."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 611600.0,
      "end_time": 614224.0,
      "text": "This is an image from a study that we conducted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 614224.0,
      "end_time": 616804.0,
      "text": "led by PhD student Micah Edelson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 616809.0,
      "end_time": 622238.0,
      "text": "and what it&#39;s showing you is a signal in the emotional center of your brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 622238.0,
      "end_time": 625211.0,
      "text": "when you hear about the opinion of others."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 625211.0,
      "end_time": 628324.0,
      "text": "And what we found was that this signal can predict"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 628324.0,
      "end_time": 631569.0,
      "text": "how likely you are to conform at a later time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 631569.0,
      "end_time": 634281.0,
      "text": "how likely you are  to change your behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 635541.0,
      "end_time": 639519.0,
      "text": "So, the British government are using this principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 639519.0,
      "end_time": 642825.0,
      "text": "to get people to pay taxes on time."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 642825.0,
      "end_time": 647551.0,
      "text": "In an old letter that they sent to people who \"forgot\" to pay taxes on time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 648150.0,
      "end_time": 650722.0,
      "text": "they simply stressed how important it was pay taxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 650722.0,
      "end_time": 652523.0,
      "text": "and that didn&#39;t help."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 652953.0,
      "end_time": 655530.0,
      "text": "Then, they added one sentence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 655662.0,
      "end_time": 657622.0,
      "text": "and that sentence said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 657622.0,
      "end_time": 662218.0,
      "text": "\"Nine out of ten people in Britain pay their taxes on time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 662218.0,
      "end_time": 667829.0,
      "text": "And that one sentence enhanced compliance within that group by 15%,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 667829.0,
      "end_time": 670373.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s thought to bring  into the British government"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 670374.0,
      "end_time": 672984.0,
      "text": "5.6 billion pounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 672984.0,
      "end_time": 677813.0,
      "text": "So, highlighting what other people  are doing is a really strong incentive."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 678420.0,
      "end_time": 681834.0,
      "text": "The other principle is immediate rewards."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 682974.0,
      "end_time": 684234.0,
      "text": "So,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 684234.0,
      "end_time": 686781.0,
      "text": "every time the staff washed their hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 686781.0,
      "end_time": 690684.0,
      "text": "they could see the numbers go up  on the board and it made them feel good."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 690684.0,
      "end_time": 693639.0,
      "text": "And knowing that in advance made them do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 693639.0,
      "end_time": 696719.0,
      "text": "that they, otherwise, may not want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 696719.0,
      "end_time": 701241.0,
      "text": "Now, this works because we value immediate rewards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 701241.0,
      "end_time": 703690.0,
      "text": "rewards that we can get now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 703700.0,
      "end_time": 706200.0,
      "text": "more than rewards that we can get in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 706920.0,
      "end_time": 710178.0,
      "text": "And people tend to think it&#39;s because we don&#39;t care about the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 710178.0,
      "end_time": 713527.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s completely wrong, we all care about our future, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 713527.0,
      "end_time": 717827.0,
      "text": "We want to be happy and healthy in the future, we want to be successful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 717835.0,
      "end_time": 719992.0,
      "text": "but the future is so far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 719992.0,
      "end_time": 724690.0,
      "text": "I mean, maybe you&#39;ll behave badly now and you&#39;ll be fine in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 724691.0,
      "end_time": 727284.0,
      "text": "and maybe you&#39;ll be altogether dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 727284.0,
      "end_time": 728720.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 728720.0,
      "end_time": 733923.0,
      "text": "So, the here-and-now you  would rather have that tangible drink,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 733923.0,
      "end_time": 735486.0,
      "text": "that tangible T-bone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 735486.0,
      "end_time": 739172.0,
      "text": "rather than something that&#39;s uncertain in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 739172.0,
      "end_time": 742232.0,
      "text": "If you think about it,  it&#39;s not altogether irrational, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 742232.0,
      "end_time": 743944.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re choosing something sure now"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 743945.0,
      "end_time": 746807.0,
      "text": "rather than something that is unsure in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 747877.0,
      "end_time": 752154.0,
      "text": "But what will happen if you reward people now"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 752154.0,
      "end_time": 755707.0,
      "text": "for doing actions that are good for them in the future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 757807.0,
      "end_time": 760756.0,
      "text": "Studies show that giving people immediate rewards"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 760756.0,
      "end_time": 763246.0,
      "text": "make them more likely to quit smoking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 763246.0,
      "end_time": 765230.0,
      "text": "more likely to start exercising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 765230.0,
      "end_time": 767986.0,
      "text": "and this effect lasts  for at least six months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 767986.0,
      "end_time": 772201.0,
      "text": "because not smoking becomes associated with a reward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 772201.0,
      "end_time": 775102.0,
      "text": "and exercising becomes associated with a reward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 775102.0,
      "end_time": 776880.0,
      "text": "and it becomes a habit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 776880.0,
      "end_time": 778782.0,
      "text": "it becomes a lifestyle."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 779633.0,
      "end_time": 781644.0,
      "text": "So, we can reward ourselves and others now"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 781644.0,
      "end_time": 784226.0,
      "text": "for behaving in ways that are good for us in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 784226.0,
      "end_time": 787416.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s a way for us to bridge the temporal gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 787416.0,
      "end_time": 790409.0,
      "text": "And the third principle is progress monitoring."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 790978.0,
      "end_time": 794334.0,
      "text": "So, the electronic board focused the medical staff attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 794335.0,
      "end_time": 796953.0,
      "text": "on improving their performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 796953.0,
      "end_time": 799553.0,
      "text": "This is an image from a study that we conducted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 799553.0,
      "end_time": 801364.0,
      "text": "that shows you brain activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 801364.0,
      "end_time": 806476.0,
      "text": "suggestive of efficient coding of positive information about the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 807406.0,
      "end_time": 811686.0,
      "text": "And what we found was that the brain does a really good job at this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 811687.0,
      "end_time": 813836.0,
      "text": "but it doesn&#39;t do such a good job"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 813836.0,
      "end_time": 816840.0,
      "text": "at processing negative information about the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 816840.0,
      "end_time": 818427.0,
      "text": "So, what does this mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 819158.0,
      "end_time": 822707.0,
      "text": "It means that, if you&#39;re trying to get people&#39;s attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 822707.0,
      "end_time": 826762.0,
      "text": "you might want to highlight  the progress, not the decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 827171.0,
      "end_time": 828575.0,
      "text": "So, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 828575.0,
      "end_time": 831199.0,
      "text": "if you take that kid with the cigarette,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 831199.0,
      "end_time": 833170.0,
      "text": "you might want to tell them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 833170.0,
      "end_time": 837216.0,
      "text": "\"You know, if you stop smoking, you&#39;ll become better at sports.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 837216.0,
      "end_time": 839888.0,
      "text": "Highlight the progress, not the decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 839888.0,
      "end_time": 843875.0,
      "text": "Now, before I sum up, let me just share this small anecdote with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 843875.0,
      "end_time": 848403.0,
      "text": "A few weeks ago, I got home and I found this bill on my fridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 848403.0,
      "end_time": 851682.0,
      "text": "And was really surprised because there&#39;s never any bills on my fridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 851682.0,
      "end_time": 855417.0,
      "text": "So, I was wondering why my husband decided to put that on our fridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 855417.0,
      "end_time": 859386.0,
      "text": "And so, looking at the bill, I could see that what this bill was trying to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 859386.0,
      "end_time": 863126.0,
      "text": "is get me to be more efficient with my electricity use."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 863126.0,
      "end_time": 865221.0,
      "text": "And how was it doing it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 865221.0,
      "end_time": 869271.0,
      "text": "Social incentives, immediate rewards and progress monitoring."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 869271.0,
      "end_time": 870257.0,
      "text": "Let me show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 870258.0,
      "end_time": 872183.0,
      "text": "Here are the social incentives."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 872183.0,
      "end_time": 874758.0,
      "text": "In gray is the energy use"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 874758.0,
      "end_time": 878110.0,
      "text": "on the average energy use  of people in my neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 878110.0,
      "end_time": 881335.0,
      "text": "And in blue is my energy use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 881335.0,
      "end_time": 884350.0,
      "text": "and in green is the most efficient neighbor."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 884761.0,
      "end_time": 886982.0,
      "text": "And my reaction to this was --"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 886982.0,
      "end_time": 888420.0,
      "text": "my immediate reaction was:"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 888420.0,
      "end_time": 890780.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m a little bit better than average\" (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 890780.0,
      "end_time": 892560.0,
      "text": "-- a tiny bit, but still..."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 892560.0,
      "end_time": 895896.0,
      "text": "and my husband had  exactly the same reaction --"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 895897.0,
      "end_time": 899109.0,
      "text": "and \"I want to get to the green bar.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 899109.0,
      "end_time": 901460.0,
      "text": "And then, I got a smiley face."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 901460.0,
      "end_time": 904856.0,
      "text": "That was my immediate reward and it was telling me, \"You&#39;re doing good,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 904856.0,
      "end_time": 907290.0,
      "text": "and it made me want to put this on my fridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 907290.0,
      "end_time": 908983.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 908983.0,
      "end_time": 911856.0,
      "text": "And although I have this one smiley face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 911856.0,
      "end_time": 915129.0,
      "text": "I can see an opportunity there to get two smiley faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 915129.0,
      "end_time": 916756.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 917566.0,
      "end_time": 919985.0,
      "text": "So, there&#39;s an opportunity for progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 919985.0,
      "end_time": 923210.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s showing me my progress throughout the year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 923210.0,
      "end_time": 925813.0,
      "text": "how my energy use changes throughout the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 925813.0,
      "end_time": 928499.0,
      "text": "And the last thing this bill gave me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 928499.0,
      "end_time": 931800.0,
      "text": "it gave me a sense of control."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 931800.0,
      "end_time": 935643.0,
      "text": "So, it gave me a sense of I was in control of my use of electricity."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 935643.0,
      "end_time": 937426.0,
      "text": "And that is a really important thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 937426.0,
      "end_time": 939805.0,
      "text": "if you try to get people to change their behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 939805.0,
      "end_time": 943563.0,
      "text": "because the brain is constantly trying to seek ways to control its environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 943563.0,
      "end_time": 947112.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s one of the principles of what the brain is actually doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 947112.0,
      "end_time": 952281.0,
      "text": "And so, giving people a sense of control is a really important motivator."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 952672.0,
      "end_time": 955400.0,
      "text": "OK. So, what am I not saying?"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 955400.0,
      "end_time": 960116.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not saying that we do not need to communicate risks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 960116.0,
      "end_time": 964221.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m not saying that there&#39;s one-solution-fits-all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 964221.0,
      "end_time": 968598.0,
      "text": "but I am saying that, if we want to motivate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 968598.0,
      "end_time": 972140.0,
      "text": "we might want to rethink how we do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 972140.0,
      "end_time": 977200.0,
      "text": "because fear, the fear of losing  your health, the fear of losing money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 977200.0,
      "end_time": 978722.0,
      "text": "induces inaction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 978722.0,
      "end_time": 982327.0,
      "text": "while the thrill of a gain induces action."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 982327.0,
      "end_time": 985948.0,
      "text": "And so, to change behavior in ourselves and in others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 985948.0,
      "end_time": 988981.0,
      "text": "we may want to try these positive strategies"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 988981.0,
      "end_time": 990702.0,
      "text": "rather than threats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 990702.0,
      "end_time": 994137.0,
      "text": "which really capitalize on the human tendency"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 994137.0,
      "end_time": 996740.0,
      "text": "to seek progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 996740.0,
      "end_time": 997296.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 997297.0,
      "end_time": 998707.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}